==Etymology==
From Latin ''[[relativus]]'', adjective form with suffix ''[[-ivus]]'', from ''[[relatus]]'', perfect passive participle of ''[[referre]]'', lit. '''carry again''', from prefix ''[[re-]]'', '''again''' + ''[[ferre]]'', '''bear''' or '''carry''', from PIE ??

